      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a Management Information Base (MIB) for configuring and managing TN3270E servers.  The MIB defined by this memo provides generic support for both host and gateway TN3270E server implementations. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
